<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Newcastle are closing on a £250,000 deal for highly-rated Peru playmaker Rodrigo Vilca from Deportivo Municipal.</p>

<p>The 21-year-old could be loaned out initially for experience.</p>

<p>The midfielder is regarded as a promising talent and has been called up to the national squad by coach Ricardo Gareca.</p>

<p>Newcastle are close to signing 21-year-old Peruvian playmaker Rodrigo Vilca</p>

<p>Newcastle fear he may lack the physical capabilities to make an impact in the Premier League just yet.</p>

